snippet.title: CodeX - Adventure game - Trailer
snippet.description:
Code X is an thrillling FPP-Adventure game made with Unreal Engine 5 by a very small indie developer.

Take a first-look at some cinematic shots and gameplay.

Code X will be available on 1st of December 2023 for Windows PC.
